{"tid":1072560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想多謝尋晚走埋嚟關心我嗰位先生","createTime":"2019-03-22T06:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T06:36:01.000Z","uid":191290,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"befd007236f43855a677ebe24159e36dad5b61d6","tid":1072560,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:01:46.000Z","msg":"話說我習慣每晚都會係屋企樓下練呼吸、拉筋咁，尋晚返part time收得比較夜，搞到點幾兩點先開始練。<br />\n<br />\n當時我聽緊歌，圍住球場一路行一路練緊腹式呼吸，可能離遠落似抽泣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，坐喺遠處有個哥哥仔望咗我兩眼，我仲心諗要小心啲。隔咗陣呢位哥哥仔行咗埋嚟坐喺球場邊個張凳同我揮手，因為塞住AirPod我聽唔到佢講咩，原本諗緊不如調頭走，個腦仲開始有小劇場（波動拳 ★ &darr;↘&rarr; + 拳）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我行到佢附近，佢又同我講嘢，我除低AirPod，佢問我：「小姐你無事吖嘛，見你行咗好多個圈，有無嘢幫到你？」噢忽，我小人之心了。我勁老尷硬生生收返9成功力，同佢講：「哈...哈..無呀無呀，我練緊呼吸之嘛..」然後佢係咁叫我加油，同埋夜啦小心啲就走咗。<br />\n<br />\n喂，我唔知你有無機會睇到，我想講我好多謝你，好開心喺呢個混亂不堪嘅世代仲有咁熱心嘅人！如果尋晚嗰個唔係我，係另一個真係情緒崩潰嘅人，你可能已經救咗佢一命。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">～～～多謝你呀！～～～</span></span>"},{"pid":"f10c68c0670e3018e1c29beb95b1d63e5a3e8c14","tid":1072560,"uid":74262,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:06:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce174d40263a940c4657ec908e71a072ca0a8d22","tid":1072560,"uid":58093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cafcf78574884b509c074dbdf51ed5fe7744b3c","tid":1072560,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"比較有興趣係點解練呼吸同拉筋要落樓下？<br />\n同埋呼吸點練法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />share吓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff46fb746fa3f32fdfbd90999226ef03c18542f","tid":1072560,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"基"},{"pid":"843ddb34e813f1470bc1ef74cc01f880e724dd3f","tid":1072560,"uid":69484,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"狗公就係咁 <br />\n好似我呢d老實好人 <br />\n只會睇佢有冇自殺既企圖 <br />\n根本唔會同佢講野"},{"pid":"80c14796cb7f0ec1675d6e9fb6563b494396a807","tid":1072560,"uid":53122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"嗰位巴打應該型英帥<br />\n<br />\n如果係肥柒毒<br />\n樓主而家就屌緊話比人嚇親<br />\n<br />\n結論：沒有對的事 只有對的人<br />\n<br />\nyour face your fate"},{"pid":"31e1235440335249679b3a7243b450b2aa8fc750","tid":1072560,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"我都會問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 始終有人喊 都畀張紙巾佢嘅<br />\n<br />\n不過練呼吸有乜用"},{"pid":"a78b8fdb0434a94be6222cb2d68898ad99bf9062","tid":1072560,"uid":202995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:36:01.000Z","msg":"香港係有好人既, 不過夜媽媽, 樓主都係小心D 好 ... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}